# Seamless API

{% hint style="warning" %}
Your site must implement this callback APIs. It is **required** for Seamless mode only.
{% endhint %}

The platform sends requests to your configured site endpoint (e.g. `https://your-backend.com/gold_api`).

{% hint style="danger" %}
When entering the Site Endpoint in profile page, ensure that it is an `https` domain and does not include `/gold_api` at the end, as `/gold_api` will be appended automatically when sending API requests.
{% endhint %}
